node.text: (link in bio) We talk about her passion for being in tune with nature. She shares how she encourages open communication with her children, appreciating nature as it is while learning to appreciate our own value, and the healing benefits of incorporating meditation in your daily routine.

node.text: Drop a ❤️ below if you’re trying this👇Non attachment has to be practiced and developed. You don’t just wake up one day and have the ability. Allow yourself to improve just a little everyday.

node.text:
@radhidevlukia Happy Birthday! 🎈🎂🎁 I am so happy you were born! My wish and prayer for you is that you continue to use your gifts and passions in the service of God & Humanity and continue to be an instrument of love and compassion. You have so much to offer the world and you’re just getting started. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
When people ask me “what’s the most exciting thing happening in your life right now?” My honest answer is, watching you grow. Watching you move outside of your comfort zone, take on new challenges, learning new skills, staying committed to your practices and becoming so passionate about helping others. It’s phenomenal to see how much you’ve accomplished in the last 12 months. And more importantly, it’s the intention and purpose with which you do it. The love and empathy through which you share. Everyone who knows you feels it. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Everyday feels like a celebration with you. You don’t wait for your birthday to dance, you don’t wait for your birthday to eat cake and you don’t wait for your birthday to celebrate. But today we are going to dance more, eat more cake and celebrate YOU more because you deserve it! I love you! Thank you for being in my life.

node.text:
Saying Yes takes determination ⁠⁠
Saying No takes courage ⁠⁠
Competing requires focus ⁠⁠
Exiting requires bravery ⁠⁠
Achievements are wonderful ⁠⁠
Acceptance is crucial ⁠⁠
Simone has shown us the power of all of these throughout her life. Thank you for allowing us to value each and every one of these choices as important. Putting yourself first before opinions, expectations and obligations takes strength. Let’s honor @simonebiles decision amidst the noise so we can learn to hear our own inner voice more clearly.
